## Purpose

Map generalized design categories for {{ project.name }}.

This optional template supports design-stage categorization only. It must not copy raw procedures, sensitive requirements, live values, operational details, or downstream-specific source content.

## Scope

- High-level category mapping.
- Synthetic input categories.
- Abstract output categories.
- Evidence/source row references.
- Open questions that require owner review.

