## Prohibited Content

- Raw source bulk copy.
- Real procedures, operational steps, or sensitive requirement text.
- Runtime implementation logic.
- C# source, solution, project, XAML, build assets, scripts, or binaries.
- PLC/device code.
- Live target write support or external mutation.
- GitHub Actions or cloud CI.
- IP, port, tag value, live parameter, secret, credential, private input, live config, or equipment detail.

## Approval Boundary

This map is a design-stage categorization artifact. It does not approve implementation, example creation, profile creation, render integration, gate implementation, or runtime behavior.

## Review Checklist

- Categories are generalized.
- Inputs are synthetic categories only.
- Outputs are abstract categories only.
- Source references use allowed source rows.
- Owner-review sources remain unused until resolved.
- Prohibited content is absent.
